			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Lithium carbonate is a chemical compound often used as an intermediate product in the processing of lithium minerals to produce various lithium-based end products. It has undergone purification and treatment to meet industry quality standards, is typically used in the manufacturing of batteries, glass, and ceramics, and serves as a precursor in pharmaceutical productions. The strength and grade of lithium carbonate can vary depending on its intended application. The product is commonly available to consumer markets and production facilities worldwide.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">碳酸锂是一种化学化合物，通常用作处理锂矿物以生产各种基于锂的最终产品的中间产品。它经过净化和处理以满足行业质量标准，通常用于制造电池、玻璃和陶瓷，并作为制药生产的前体。碳酸锂的强度和等级可根据其预定用途而有所不同。该产品通常可在全球消费市场和生产设施中获取。</common:generalComment>
